---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms and Conditions" description="Expert Guru Terms and Conditions - Read our terms of service.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-linear-to-br from-primary/10 via-white to-secondary/10 py-20">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Terms and Conditions</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Welcome to Expert Guru!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          These Terms and Conditions (&quot;Terms&quot;) govern your use of our website, services, and any content provided by Expert Guru (&quot;we,&quot; &quot;our,&quot; or &quot;us&quot;). By accessing or using our website (www.expertguru.net) or enrolling in any of our services, you agree to abide by these Terms. If you do not agree, please do not use our services or website.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Use of Website and Services</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              By accessing our website or registering for our services, you agree that all information you provide is accurate and current. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account and any activity that occurs under it.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Services Offered</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Expert Guru provides academic tutoring and test preparation services including but not limited to SAT/ACT Prep, College Admissions Counseling, Essay Writing Assistance, and Subject Tutoring. Services may be offered in-person or online, depending on availability and location.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Payment and Refund Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Our pricing is based on monthly packages, and the cost varies depending on the number of hours you purchase. We offer a 100% money-back guarantee for new students within the first four sessions or two weeks of starting the program, whichever comes first. You can contact our enrollment team for detailed pricing information.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              All content on our website, including text, graphics, videos, logos, and course materials, is the property of Expert Guru and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws. You may not copy, reproduce, modify, distribute, or use any content for commercial purposes without prior written consent.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">User Conduct</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">You agree not to:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-red-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
                <span>Use our website or services for any unlawful purpose</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-red-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
                <span>Disrupt or interfere with the security or functionality of the website</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-red-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
                <span>Upload or transmit any harmful material such as viruses or malicious code</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-red-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
                <span>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems or user data</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              While we strive to provide high-quality educational services, Expert Guru makes no guarantees regarding test score improvements or admissions outcomes. We are not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our website or services.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Third-Party Links</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Our website may include links to third-party websites for your convenience. We do not control or endorse the content of these sites and are not responsible for any issues arising from their use.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Modifications to Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We reserve the right to update or modify these Terms at any time without prior notice. The updated Terms will be posted on this page with the revised date. Continued use of our services after changes are made indicates your acceptance of the new Terms.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Termination</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your access to our services or website if you violate these Terms or engage in behavior deemed harmful to our students, staff, or brand.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Governing Law</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              These Terms are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Texas, without regard to its conflict of law principles. Any disputes shall be resolved in the courts of Fort Bend County, Texas.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-linear-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-2xl p-8 text-white">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="text-white/90 mb-4">If you have any questions about these Terms and Conditions, please contact us:</p>
            <p class="font-semibold">Expert Guru</p>
            <p class="text-white/90">Email: <a href="mailto:info@expertguru.net" class="underline">info@expertguru.net</a></p>
            <p class="text-white/90">Website: <a href="https://www.expertguru.net" class="underline">www.expertguru.net</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
